        swaccess: "rw0c",
        hwaccess: "none",
        fields: [
          { bits:   "0",
            desc: '''
            When cleared to 0, !!INTEGRITY_CHECK_PERIOD and !!CONSISTENCY_CHECK_PERIOD registers cannot be written anymore.
